org.hms.services.medicalrecord

Packages that use org.hms.services.medicalrecord
Package
Description
org.hms
This package contains the main classes for the Hospital Management System (HMS).
org.hms.services.medicalrecord
Provides services related to medical records.
org.hms.services.storage
This package contains the storage service classes for the Hospital Management System (HMS).
  • Classes in org.hms.services.medicalrecord used by org.hms
    Class
    Description
    MedicalRecordService
    MedicalRecordService is responsible for managing medical records, personal particulars, and contact information related to patients in the system.
  • Classes in org.hms.services.medicalrecord used by org.hms.services.medicalrecord
    Class
    Description
    ContactInformation
    The ContactInformation class represents the contact details of a patient, including their phone number, email, and address.
    ContactInformationTable
    This class represents a table of contact information, providing functionality to manage, format, and render contact entries such as phone numbers and emails.
    IMedicalDataInterface
    This interface should be implemented by StorageService.
    MedicalEntry
    The MedicalEntry class represents a record of a medical consultation which includes details such as patient ID, doctor ID, date of consultation, diagnosis, treatment plan, and consultation notes.
    MedicalRecord
    This class represents a medical record which contains a collection of medical entries.
    PatientParticulars
    The PatientParticulars class represents the details of a patient, including their ID, name, date of birth, gender, and blood type.
    PatientTable
    The PatientTable class extends AbstractTable to provide a specialized table for patient particulars.
